@ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5127
@approverToken = paste-approver-token-here
@developerToken = paste-developer-token-here
@devPromotionId = paste-dev-promotion-id-here
@stagingPromotionId = paste-staging-promotion-id-here
@productionPromotionId = paste-production-promotion-id-here
@roleTestPromotionId = paste-promotion-id-here
@conflictPromotionId = paste-promotion-id-here
@conflictingPromotionId = paste-promotion-id-here

###

### 1. Get approver token
POST {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "approver"
}

###

### 2. Get developer token
POST {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "developer"
}

###

### 3. Request dev promotion - no sourceEnvironment, dev is the first environment
POST {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{developerToken}}

{
  "applicationId": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "version": "1.2.3",
  "targetEnvironment": "dev",
  "issueReferences": ["PROJ-101", "PROJ-102", "PROJ-103"]
}

###

### 4. Approve dev promotion - paste id from request 3 into @devPromotionId
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{devPromotionId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 5. Start dev deployment - transitions Approved to InProgress
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{devPromotionId}}/start
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 6. Complete dev promotion - transitions InProgress to Completed, unlocks staging
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{devPromotionId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 7. Request staging promotion - sourceEnvironment dev satisfies the predecessor check
POST {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{developerToken}}

{
  "applicationId": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "version": "1.2.3",
  "sourceEnvironment": "dev",
  "targetEnvironment": "staging",
  "issueReferences": ["PROJ-101", "PROJ-102", "PROJ-103"]
}

###

### 8. Approve staging promotion - paste id from request 7 into @stagingPromotionId
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{stagingPromotionId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 9. Start staging deployment - transitions Approved to InProgress
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{stagingPromotionId}}/start
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 10. Complete staging promotion - transitions InProgress to Completed
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{stagingPromotionId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 11. Request production promotion - staging must be completed first
POST {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{developerToken}}

{
  "applicationId": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "version": "1.2.3",
  "sourceEnvironment": "staging",
  "targetEnvironment": "production",
  "issueReferences": ["PROJ-101", "PROJ-102", "PROJ-103"]
}

###

### 12. Approve production promotion
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{productionPromotionId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 13. Start production deployment
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{productionPromotionId}}/start
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 14. Complete production promotion
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{productionPromotionId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

### 15. Get promotion by id - returns PromotionDetailDto with full state history
GET {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{stagingPromotionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 16. Get environment status - returns current state per environment for the application
GET {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa/environment-status
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 17. List promotions by application - paged, returns PromotionSummaryDto list
GET {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions?applicationId=aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 18. Request promotion for role enforcement test - paste id into @roleTestPromotionId
POST {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{developerToken}}

{
  "applicationId": "bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb",
  "version": "2.0.0",
  "targetEnvironment": "dev"
}

###

### 18b. Approve with developer token - expect 401 Unauthorized (domain role check)
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{roleTestPromotionId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{developerToken}}

###

### 19. Cancel completed promotion - expect 409 Conflict (invalid state transition)
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{stagingPromotionId}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

{
  "reason": "Trying to cancel a completed promotion"
}

###

### 20a. Request promotion for conflict test - paste id into @conflictPromotionId
POST {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{developerToken}}

{
  "applicationId": "cccccccc-cccc-cccc-cccc-cccccccccccc",
  "version": "3.0.0",
  "targetEnvironment": "dev"
}

###

### 20b. Approve conflict promotion - moves to Approved
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{conflictPromotionId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 20c. Start conflict promotion - moves to InProgress, slot is now occupied
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{conflictPromotionId}}/start
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}

###

### 20d. Request second promotion for same app - paste id into @conflictingPromotionId
POST {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{developerToken}}

{
  "applicationId": "cccccccc-cccc-cccc-cccc-cccccccccccc",
  "version": "3.0.1",
  "targetEnvironment": "dev"
}

###

### 20e. Approve while first is InProgress - expect 409 Conflict (slot occupied)
PUT {{ReleasePilot.Api_HostAddress}}/api/promotions/{{conflictingPromotionId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{approverToken}}
